Several methods have been proposed to deal with anaphora resolution and prepositional phrase (PP) attachment phenomenon and separately, so that the literature is very abundant : for PPs see e.g., (Frazier and Fodor, 1979; Hobbs, 1990), and (Wilks and Huang, 1985), and for anaphora see e.g., (Carter, 1986; Reinhart, 1983) and (Sidner, 1983).
